'''Green Squad 7''' was one of eight [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] training squads who trained at [[Alliance Training Center-5/Green Squad]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ksift]]. When the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] attacked the base, an initiate of this squad met with a group of trainees from [[Green Squad]] who would go on to become [[Green Squad 3]] and told them that their help was needed out front to combat the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces.

